
* To add a task:

./status.rb n[ew] some task description

* To list tasks:

./status.rb l[ist]

* To start a task:

./status.rb s[tart] <num>

* To finish a task:

./status.rb f[inish] <num>

* To unstart a task:

./status.rb u[nstart] <num>

* To delete a task:

./status.rb d[elete] <num>

* To print status:

./status.rb p

(This copies status to the clipboard if you have xclip).

